hive-date=August 14, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Ethan Klein}}\n* {{Official website|1=http://www.h3h3productions.com/}}\n* {{YouTube channel|u=h3h3Productions}}\n* {{Twitter}}\n* {{Discord|https://discord.gg/h3h3}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:American YouTubers]]\n[[Category:Jewish artists]]\n[[Category:Jewish American artists]]\n[[Category:Jewish American comedians]]\n[[Category:Jewish American entertainers]]\n[[Category:Twitch streamers]]\n[[Category:Video game commentators]]\n[[Category:YouTube channels launched in 2013]]\n[[Category:Comedy-related YouTube channels]]\n[[Category:American podcasters]]\n[[Category:YouTube podcasters]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Comedy YouTube channel}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=April 2017}}\n{{Lowercase title}}\n{{Infobox YouTube personality\n|name              = h3h3Productions\n|logo              = h3h3Productions logo.jpg\n|logo_size         = 120px\n|image             =\n|image_size        =\n|caption           = h3h3Productions logo\n|birth_name        = {{plainlist|style=text-indent:-1em; margin-left:1em;|\n*Ethan Edward Klein<br>{{birth date and age|1985|06|25}}<br>[[Ventura, California]], U.S.\n*Hila Hakmon<br>{{birth date and age|1987|12|12}}<br>[[Holon, Israel]]\n}}\n|nationality       = [[United States|American]] and [[Israel]]i (dual citizenship)\n|residence         = [[Los Angeles]], [[California]], U.S.\n|education         = [[University of California, Santa Cruz]] (Ethan)<br>[[Shenkar College of Engineering and Design]] (Hila)\n|channel_name      = h3h3Productions\n|years_active      = 2011\u2013present\n|genre             = {{hlist|[[Comedy]]|[[satire]]|[[Reaction video|reaction]]|[[vlog]]}}\n|subscribers       = 6,590,264 subscribers\n|views             = 1,397,168,390 views\n|associated_acts   = {{hlist||[[Joji (musician)|Filthy Frank]]||[[iDubbbz]]||[[Jacksepticeye]]||[[JonTron]]||[[Justin Roiland]]||[[PewDiePie]]||[[Philip DeFranco]]||[[Post Malone]]