ublisher=Twitter|accessdate=April 22, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602074741/https://twitter.com/HilaKleinH3/status/590821010624024576|archive-date=June 2, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"NYC\">{{cite web|author=Ethan and Hila|date=September 9, 2015|url=//www.youtube.com/watch?v=SlLq8PY9mQ8|title=The Pope is coming to town|publisher=Youtube|accessdate=September 9, 2015}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Bye NYC\">{{cite web|author=h3h3productions|date=August 14, 2016|url=//www.youtube.com/watch?v=10BxccZP1kE|title=Goodbye New York|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=August 14, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160814191918/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=10BxccZP1kE|archive-date=August 14, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Ethan Klein}}\n* {{Official website|1=http://www.h3h3productions.com/}}\n* {{YouTube channel|u=h3h3Productions}}\n* {{Twitter}}\n* {{Discord|https://discord.gg/h3h3}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:American YouTubers]]\n[[Category:Jewish artists]]\n[[Category:Jewish American artists]]\n[[Category:Jewish American comedians]]\n[[Category:Jewish American entertainers]]\n[[Category:Twitch streamers]]\n[[Category:Video game commentators]]\n[[Category:YouTube channels launched in 2013]]\n[[Category:Comedy-related YouTube channels]]\n[[Category:American podcasters]]\n[[Category:YouTube podcasters]]\n", "name_user": "Bobby108517", "label": "safe", "comment": "Removed unnecessary fluff. Information about the channel\u2019s name being tied to Ethan and Hila\u2019s initials is already in the article one sentence below the information I removed.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/H3h3Productions"}
